rComments: Christopher Lee is one of the best professors you will find in undergrad physics here. Amazing lecturer and prof. He has high standards, but they are achievable if you really like the materials or this course. He is always around to help and he can help you in a very efficient and constructive manner. Also got a great sense of humor.

The course was lab-heavy, but he was extremely helpful. He held a lot of office hours and was always willing to help. He pushed a due date back during exam season, and is understanding. Best professor!
